y, <strong>split shipments</strong>, or <strong>multi-location</strong> drops before placing large orders.</p>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500\">Minimum order quantity: <strong class=\"text-neutral-800\">1</strong> units (per catalog line).</p>\n</div>"}